## Context
Read RULES.md first, then CLAUDE.md (project status), then PROTOCOL.md (pipeline entry point).
Unknown terms → GLOSSARY.md.

## This project
TrpB MetaDynamics replication for Caltech aNima Lab summer research.
Strict replication of JACS 2019 (Osuna). GROMACS + PLUMED2 for MetaD, AMBER 24p3 for system prep.
All campaigns defined in replication/manifests/. Do not execute without a frozen manifest.

## Rules
- Chinese for explanations, English for technical terms and commands
- Give one clear entry point at a time, not 20 files at once
- Always explain why before doing it (> blockquote format)
- Mark unfinished steps as NOT STARTED — never fake progress
- Code blocks: give the command directly, don't describe it

## Current campaign
replication/manifests/osuna2019_benchmark_manifest.yaml — status: parameters-confirmed
Next: toy MetaD test (alanine dipeptide on Longleaf) → 1WDW/3CEP download → PLP parameterization
